description: Data models used across the TV app, representing content items, channels, programs, and categories.

classes.name: ContentItem
classes.description: Represents a content item (VOD or live) with attributes like id, title, description, duration, poster, categories, and stream URL.

classes.name: Channel
classes.description: Represents a TV channel with attributes like id, number, name, logo URL, and stream URL.

classes.name: Program
classes.description: An EPG program airing on a channel with attributes such as id, channelId, title, description, start and end times.

classes.name: Category
classes.description: Represents a category of content rows on Home with a name.
